<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. التَّارِكِينَ لِكُلِّ فِعْلٍ سَيءٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَالْعَامِلِينَ بِأَحْسَنِ الأَعْمَالِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَهْوَاءُهُمْ تَبَعٌ لِدِينِ نَبِيِّهِمْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَسِوَاهُمْ بِالضِّدِّ مِنْ ذِي الْحَالِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مَا شَابَهُمْ فِي دِينِهِمْ نَقْصٌ وَلا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فِي قَوْلِهِمْ شَطْحُ الْجَهُولِ الْغَالِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عَمِلُوا بِمَا عَلِمُوا وَلَمْ يَتَكَلَّفُوا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَلِذَاكَ مَا شَابُوا الْهُدَى بِضَلالِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَسِوَاهُمُ بِالضِّدِ فِي أَحْوَالِهِمْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>تَرَكُوا الْهُدَى وَدَعَوا إِلَى الضَّلالِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَهُمْ الأَذِلَّةُ لِلْحَيَارَى مَن يَسِرْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِهُدَاهُمُ لَمْ يَخْشَ مِنْ إِضْلالِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَهُمُ النُّجُومُ هِدَايَةً وَإِضَاءَةً<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَعُلُو مَنْزِلَةٍ وَبُعْدَ مَنَالِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>يَمْشُونَ بَيْنَ النَّاسِ هَوْنًا نُطْقُهُمْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>بِالْحَقِّ لا بِجَهَالَةِ الْجُهَّالِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>حَلِمًا وَعِلْمًا مَعَ تُقَىً وَتَوَاضِعِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَنَصِيحَةٍ مَعَ رُتْبَةِ الإِفْضَالِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>يُحْيُونَ لَيْلَهُمْ بِطَاعَةِ رَبِّهِمْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>بِتِلاوَةٍ وَتَضَرُّعٍ وَسُؤَالِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَعُيُونُهُمْ تَجْرِي بِفَيْضِ دُمُوعِهِمْ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>مِثْلَ انْهِمَالِ الْوَابِلِ الْهَلالِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>